{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"HXL hashtag word clouds","content":"<div>\r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n    <a href=\"https://se.linkedin.com/in/henrik-sjokvist\">Henrik Sj√∂kvist</a>, a volunteer at the <a href=\"https://centre.humdata.org\">Centre for Humanitarian Data</a>, has put together preliminary word clouds for the human-readable text headers associated with different hashtags in the <a href=\"https://data.humdata.org/search?tags=hxl\">HXL datasets on the Humanitarian Data Exchange (HDX)</a>. These images do not (yet) take attributes into account, but they provide an interesting insight into how people are using the <a href=\"http://hxl.local\">HXL humanitarian data standard</a> in the wild.\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n    You might also be interested in <a href=\"https://tools.humdata.org/examples/hxl/\">HXL Tag Assist</a>, which shows HXL hashtags in the context of the datasets using them.\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n  <p>\r\n    <i>Skip ahead to a hashtag category: <a href=\"#places\">places</a> | <a href=\"#surveys\">survey data</a> | <a href=\"#crises\">crises</a> | <a href=\"#responses\">humanitarian responses</a> | <a href=\"#metadata\">metadata</a></i>\r\n  </p>\r\n\r\n  <section id=\"places\">\r\n    <h2>Hashtags about places</h2>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"region\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_region\">#region</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudregion.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudregion.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-825\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudregion.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudregion-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudregion-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"adm3\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_adm3\">#adm3</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudadm3.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudadm3.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-835\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudadm3.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudadm3-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudadm3-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"loc\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_loc\">#loc</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudloc.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudloc.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-842\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudloc.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudloc-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudloc-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"geo\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_geo\">#geo</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgeo.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgeo.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-843\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgeo.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgeo-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgeo-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n  </section>\r\n  \r\n  <section id=\"surveys\">\r\n    <h2>Hashtags about survey data</h2>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"indicator\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_indicator\">#indicator</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudindicator.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudindicator.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-833\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudindicator.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudindicator-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudindicator-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"population\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_population\">#population</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudpopulation.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudpopulation.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-831\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudpopulation.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudpopulation-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudpopulation-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"inneed\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_inneed\">#inneed</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudinneed.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudinneed.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-839\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudinneed.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudinneed-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudinneed-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"targeted\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_targeted\">#targeted</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudtargeted.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudtargeted.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-838\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudtargeted.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudtargeted-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudtargeted-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"reached\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_reached\">#reached</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudreached.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudreached.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-826\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudreached.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudreached-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudreached-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n    \r\n  </section>\r\n  \r\n  <section id=\"crises\">\r\n    <h2>Hashtags about crises</h2>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"group\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_group\">#group</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgroup.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgroup.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-827\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgroup.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgroup-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudgroup-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"event\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_event\">#event</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudevent.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudevent.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-844\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudevent.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudevent-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudevent-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n  </section>\r\n\r\n  <section id=\"responses\">\r\n    <h2>Hashtags about humanitarian responses</h2>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"value\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_value\">#value</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudvalue.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudvalue.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-829\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudvalue.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudvalue-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudvalue-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"status\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_status\">#status</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudstatus.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudstatus.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-830\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudstatus.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudstatus-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudstatus-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"org\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_org\">#org</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudorg.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudorg.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-832\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudorg.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudorg-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudorg-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"sector\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_sector\">#sector</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsector.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsector.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-840\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsector.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsector-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsector-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n    \r\n    <section id=\"subsector\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_subsector\">#subsector</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsubsector.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsubsector.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-824\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsubsector.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsubsector-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudsubsector-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"activity\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_activity\">#activity</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudactivity.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudactivity.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-837\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudactivity.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudactivity-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudactivity-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n  </section>\r\n\r\n  <section id=\"metadata\">\r\n    <h2>Metadata hashtags</h2>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"meta\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_meta\">#meta</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudmeta.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudmeta.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-841\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudmeta.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudmeta-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordcloudmeta-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n    <section id=\"description\">\r\n      <h3><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/standard/1_1final/dictionary/#tag_description\">#description</a></h3>\r\n\r\n      <a target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordclouddescription.png\"><img src=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordclouddescription.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"alignright size-medium wp-image-834\" srcset=\"http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordclouddescription.png 640w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordclouddescription-300x225.png 300w, http://hxl.local/wp-content/uploads/wordclouddescription-624x468.png 624w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\" /></a>\r\n    </section>\r\n\r\n  </section>\r\n\r\n  <section id=\"more\">\r\n    <h2>More about HXL</h2>\r\n\r\n    <p>\r\n      If you&#8217;re interested in learning more about HXL, you are welcome to visit <a href=\"http://hxl.local\">hxlstandard.org</a>, join the public <a href=\"https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/hxlproject\">hxlproject@googlegroups.com</a> mailing list, and watch the <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/hxl\">#HXL</a> hashtag on Twitter.\r\n    </p>\r\n\r\n</div>"}},"pageContext":{"id":"2c3ed5ff-99b9-528c-915c-ffd3258c9255"}}